# Gmail
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User guoweis@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mbsync/guoweis@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
SubFolders Legacy

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All
